<br>
I would like to propose that several (3-5) guilds get together and try and form an alliance with the only purpose to get past some of these Tier 2 boss mobs, and get most of these guilds members flagged for Tier 3.  <br>
<br>
Important to note this is NOT an Alliance for anything beyond PoP mobs.  This is hoping to free up space camps in PoS, PoV and give people a chance to see spectral parchments, patterns etc. that only drop in XP groups/Mini Boss mobs that drop in Tier 3 zones.<br>
<br>
As an aside, most of these mobs have been brought down on other serers by OPEN raids.  It might take us a while but we can get more people flagged for Tier 3 working together than apart.  <br>
<br>
Please post here or send me a tell in game if this interests any other guild.<br>
<br>
